The paper proposes a novel network structure for accelerating the inference process of convolutional neural networks, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also discusses the implementation of low-cost collaborative layers, which falls under the category of neural networks (cs.NE) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). Finally, the paper evaluates its proposed method on image classification benchmarks, which is a common task in natural language processing (cs.CL) and computer vision (cs.CV).
